cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.DS, cs.SE 

This paper discusses the comparison of different methods for managing uncertainty in expert systems, which is a common topic in the field of artificial intelligence (AI). Therefore, cs.AI is the most likely sub-category. The study also involves learning trials and performance comparison, which are related to machine learning (cs.LG) and statistical inference (cs.SI). The use of different uncertain inference systems also involves data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). Finally, the study involves the development of expert systems, which is a topic in software engineering (cs.SE).
